# Project Instructions — solarx-tuya-integration

> This file is read by Cursor IDE, Windsurf, Cline, and other AI coding assistants.

## Project Root

All source code is inside `smart-charge-glow/`.
**Always work from `smart-charge-glow/` as the project root.**

```
solarx-tuya-integration/
└── smart-charge-glow/   ← actual project root
    ├── src/
    ├── package.json
    └── vite.config.ts
```

## Commands (run from `smart-charge-glow/`)

```bash
bun dev          # Start dev server (Vite + HMR)
bun build        # Production build (Nitro + Vercel)
bun build:dev    # Dev mode build
bun preview      # Preview production build
bun lint         # ESLint check
bun format       # Prettier format
```

> Bun = package manager. Build toolchain = Vite + Nitro. Not Bun runtime.

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | TanStack Start (full-stack React) |
| Routing | @tanstack/react-router (file-based) |
| Data Fetching | @tanstack/react-query + server functions |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 |
| UI Components | Radix UI + shadcn/ui |
| Charts | Recharts |
| Forms | React Hook Form + Zod |
| Notifications | Sonner |
| Server Runtime | Nitro → Vercel |
| IoT API | Tuya Cloud API (HMAC-SHA256) |
| Language | TypeScript (strict, no `any`) |
| Fonts | IBM Plex Sans Thai, JetBrains Mono |

## Directory Structure

```
src/
├── routes/               # File-based routes (auto-registered)
│   ├── __root.tsx        # Root layout + providers
│   ├── index.tsx         # Dashboard (main page)
│   ├── history.tsx       # Charging history
│   ├── settings.tsx      # App settings
│   ├── device-info.tsx   # Device information
│   └── debug.tsx         # Debug tools
├── components/
│   ├── ui/               # shadcn/ui components — do NOT modify directly
│   ├── app-shell.tsx     # Main layout wrapper
│   ├── alert-banner.tsx
│   └── page-header.tsx
├── hooks/
│   └── use-mobile.tsx    # Responsive breakpoint
├── lib/
│   ├── tuya/             # Tuya IoT integration
│   │   ├── api.functions.ts  # Server functions — Tuya API proxy
│   │   ├── client.ts         # OAuth + HMAC-SHA256 signing
│   │   ├── server.ts         # Server-side helpers
│   │   ├── mock.ts           # Mock data for dev
│   │   └── types.ts          # TypeScript types
│   ├── app-settings.tsx  # Global settings context
│   ├── alerts.ts
│   ├── error-capture.ts
│   ├── error-page.ts
│   ├── lovable-error-reporting.ts
│   └── utils.ts          # Shared utils (cn, etc.)
├── router.tsx
├── routeTree.gen.ts      # AUTO-GENERATED — never edit
├── server.ts             # SSR handler + error normalization
├── start.ts              # TanStack Start + middleware
└── styles.css            # Global styles + Tailwind
```

## Critical Rules

- **Path alias**: `@/` → `src/`
- **No `any`**: Strict TypeScript — no `any`, no `@ts-ignore` ever
- **Server-only API**: Tuya calls must use `'use server'` — never call from client code
- **routeTree.gen.ts**: Auto-generated by TanStack Router — never edit manually
- **vite.config.ts**: Uses `@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config` — do NOT add duplicate plugins
- **shadcn/ui**: Use `src/components/ui/` as-is — add via CLI only
- **Mock mode**: `src/lib/tuya/mock.ts` for offline dev

## ⚠️ Lovable Integration Warning

This project is connected to [Lovable](https://lovable.dev).
- **NEVER force push, rebase, amend, or squash pushed commits**
- All pushed commits auto-sync to Lovable
- Keep branch in working/buildable state always

